    "description": {
      "value": "<em>You have mastered the nagaji warrior technique of spitting venom into your opponent's eyes.</em><br/><br/><b>Prerequisites</b><br/>Nagaji.<br/><br/><b>Benefits</b><br/>As a full-round action, you can spit poison up to 10 feet as a ranged touch attack. If you hit, the target must make a successful Fortitude save or be blinded for 1d6 rounds. The DC of this save is equal to 10 + 1/2 your total Hit Dice + your Constitution modifier. You can use this ability once per day plus one additional time per day for every three Hit Dice you have.<br/><br/><b>Combat Trick</b><br/>When you spit poison, you can spend up to 5 stamina points. For each stamina point spent, you can increase the range of the attack by 5 feet.",
